# Tooltip

The Tooltip component contains brief messages that appear in response to a user action. A tip can be used on any screen and can be implemented anywhere on the screen, making it more contextually relevant than a dialog.

## Installation & Import

```bash
yarn add @ids-ts/tooltip
```

```tsx
import { Tooltip } from '@ids-ts/tooltip';
```

