| `onCloseButtonKeyDown` | `React.KeyboardEventHandler` | No | Handle that is fired when any keydown event fire on close icon control in tooltip. |
| `onKeyDown` | `React.KeyboardEventHandler` | No | Handler that's fired when any keydown event fire on Tooltip content. |
| `onShow` | `ReactEventHandler` | No | Called when tooltip opened. |
